description:
Business success tips in the palm of your hand!  At Entrepreneur we celebrate the spirit of creativity, curiosity and innovation. Our pages are filled with practical tips that extend to brave new ways of thinking. From Richard Branson to Peter Diamondis, we profile the people and ideas breaking down barriers and creating new opportunities.

Our goal is to empower readers and challenge traditional thinking. We invite you to join us at Entrepreneur where business, economics and pop culture intersect. This is not your father’s business magazine.

====

Subscriptions: 1 year subscription for $9.99, monthly for $1.99 or a single issue for $4.99.

Subscriptions will start from the most current issue going forward for one year from the date of purchase. Your subscription will automatically renew via your iTunes account 24-hours prior to the end of your subscription at the rate of $11.99 for a one year subscription. You can turn off the auto-renew feature up to 24-hours before the end of your subscription by going to your Account Settings after purchase. Subscriptions cannot be cancelled during the active subscription period.

For all iPad related inquiries, please visit our Customer Support Center at www.entrepreneur.com/contact-us/feedback
releaseNotes:
December 2014: Issue Snapshot
At year-end, Entrepreneur reflects on the events of 2014 and how business owners can move their companies forward in 2015. See the 10 business leaders who dominated headlines this year and those who will set the stage for the one ahead—for better or for worse. In the annual Trends feature, get a glimpse into some of the changes that will dramatically affect the business climate for the next 12 months or more. Plus,Entrepreneur looks at the wealth of business incubators and maker communities that help non-techie pursuits, such as fashion, food and other physical-product sectors. And just in time for the holiday season, the Tech department rounds up shiny objects any entrepreneur would love to give and receive.

We’ve listened to your feedback and have some exciting changes:

Free access to content!
- browse any issue in a time-limited session
- no registration or payment required
- explore content without any obligation
- super accelerated download speeds
